{"tid":2236925,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"資深製作人楊紹鴻細數廿年電視大戰：膠劇冇得救","createTime":"2020-10-10T00:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T18:56:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d4c9ab8b2addd9552d5d13e4e4b426b4fdafa1","tid":2236925,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T00:36:41.000Z","msg":"楊紹鴻昔日在電視台合作過的周潤發、劉德華和黎明，粒粒皆星，問他對今時今日電視台花旦小生有何看法？楊紹鴻說：「呢十年八年嚟講，香港電視行業係可悲，以前嘅藝人都係紅褲仔出身，由茄哩啡開始捱起，到佢成功；而家唔同以前，一個選美，一個甚麼先生就彈出嚟做主角，我之前睇到都笑，鬼妹做古裝，我覺得大鑊喇，香港嘅電視行業就係咁先，再加上大台有好多人事上嘅問題，好多山頭，但冇辦法，一個大機構實有呢啲事發生，要睇決策者點去平衡，但係平衡得唔好。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201010/65S24TM7JFBPZAZTQ7EOPRLUN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201010%2F65S24TM7JFBPZAZTQ7EOPRLUN4%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzpFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=08e22c12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201010%2F65S24TM7JFBPZAZTQ7EOPRLUN4%2F&h=7623828b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201010/65S24TM7JFBPZAZTQ7EOPRLUN4/</a>"},{"pid":"34146d5641ac7979e9ea37634bb8237e2553fb29","tid":2236925,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"又9up<br />\n選美出黎做主角廿幾三十年前已經係啦"},{"pid":"dad9939b44d3ebae4b87d88035bb71ad8e919a18","tid":2236925,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"以前勝在有勁人老戲骨帶入戲，所以選美出身都冇咩大問題<br />\n但而家就算藝訓出身都唔好得去邊，更加唔好講選美嗰班"},{"pid":"3cc216745580e8aadfe17ff98f16a1d30d6779bb","tid":2236925,"uid":31017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34146d5641ac7979e9ea37634bb8237e2553fb29","tid":2236925,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"又9up<br />\n選美出黎做主角廿幾三十年前已經係啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"張曼玉夠係選美出身<br />\n吹得就吹<br />\n屌<br />\n港姐亞姐大撚把"},{"pid":"4802